HEADWORD: Deathblow
<hw>Death"blow`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mortal or
crushing blow; a stroke or event which kills or destroys.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

